## 3. Naming Conventions

| Context | Convention | Example |
|---|---|---|
| TypeScript variables | camelCase | `salePrice`, `marginPct` |
| TypeScript types/interfaces | PascalCase | `Product`, `CreateProductDTO` |
| Database tables | snake_case | `price_history`, `economic_indices` |
| Database columns | snake_case | `user_id`, `min_margin_pct` |
| API routes | kebab-case | `/api/price-lists`, `/api/bulk-update` |
| React components | PascalCase | `ProductForm`, `MarginBadge` |
| React hooks | camelCase with `use` prefix | `useProducts`, `useAuth` |
| Files (components) | PascalCase | `ProductForm.tsx` |
| Files (hooks/utils) | camelCase | `useProducts.ts`, `pricing.ts` |
| Environment variables (api) | UPPER_SNAKE_CASE | `SUPABASE_URL`, `JWT_SECRET` |
| Environment variables (web) | `VITE_` prefix | `VITE_API_URL`, `VITE_SUPABASE_URL` |
| Git commits | English, conventional commits | `feat: add bulk update endpoint` |
| Code comments | Spanish | `// Calcula el precio de venta con el margen aplicado` |

